definitions.definition: The outer aperture of the ear; the entrance to the ear canal .
examples: What role does the wax in your earhole fulfill?

definitions.definition: A puncture in the ear, usually in the earlobe , such as for earrings .
An opening in a head-covering, such as a hat or helmet, for the ears.
